# Feedback

The API response is not final, but represents the values which go into the final response. I'd like specific request from the proofs team for their ideal oranization of this data. I can make a `min` for each grouping, and will likely remove CurrentL1s, since it is only the *locally derived* view and doesn't contain verification.
